ActMuseums Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Canadian Heritage of PETER GORDON CATHCART, Q.C., of Toronto, Ontario, as a trustee of the Board of Trustees of the National Gallery of Canada to hold office during pleasure for a term of two years, in the place of Ardyth Webster Brott.
